OL,5, Liz Truss has said she wants to save   
OL,6, taxpayers' money by ending national pay
OL,7, deals for civil servants' pay.         
OL,9,FThe Tory leadership candidate wants to 
OL,10,Flink civil servants' salaries to living
OL,11,Fstandards where they work, meaning     
OL,12,Fsimilar jobs could have different      
OL,13,Fsalaries depending on location.        
OL,15,FMs Truss says the scheme could be      
OL,16,Frolled out to other public sector      
OL,17,Fareas, saving #8.8bn a year.           
OL,19,FLabour called her plan "a fantasy      
OL,20,Frecipe for levelling down".            
